ence%20who%20have%20done%20this%20before%20do%20not%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kevin%20Desai%2C%20the%20head%20of%20tax%20and%20consulting%20firm%20PWC's%20private-equity%20consulting%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22329923da-0b9e-4780-9a1f-7f3c5e56e569%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20investment-bank%20pathway%20for%20junior%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestment%20banks%20are%20the%20most%20common%20route%20for%20young%20people%20to%20move%20to%20so-called%20buyside%20firms%2C%20whether%20a%20hedge%20fund%20or%20a%20private%20equity%20shop.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20private%20credit%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-headhunters-bonkers-hiring-market-investment-banking-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20banking%20analyst%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20proven%20such%20a%20great%20training%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20skillsets%20are%20evaluating%20whether%20a%20company%20is%20going%20to%20make%20money%2C%20how%20the%20firm%20can%20structure%20an%20investment%20to%20make%20money%2C%20and%20how%20to%20protect%20yourself%20from%20the%20downside%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Jennifer%20Cragin%2C%20a%20search%20consultant%20at%20BellCast%20partners%20who%20formerly%20was%20a%20director%20of%20the%20capital%20markets%20group%20at%20Lazard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20the%20skills%20young%20financial%20professionals%20tend%20to%20learn%20in%20investment%20banking%20or%20credit%20underwriting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20banking%20roles%20firms%20will%20want%20to%20see%20on%20a%20resume%20may%20vary%2C%20but%20all%20three%20recruiters%20said%20a%20background%20in%20leveraged%20finance%20can%20be%20very%20helpful.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-leveraged-finance-bankers-from-goldman-sachs-to-kkr-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeveraged%20finance%2C%20or%20LevFin%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20part%20of%20the%20bank%20that%20helps%20to%20finance%20private-equity%20buyouts%20and%20other%20transactions%20through%20debt.%20Bankers%20in%20leveraged%20finance%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20underwrite%20loans%20and%20predict%20future%20cash%20flow%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20direct%20banking%20analog%20to%20private%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20those%20roles%2C%20extensive%20debt%20experience%20in%20a%20particular%20line%20of%20business%20can%20help%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20aligns%20with%20an%20industry%20that%20the%20potential%20employer%20is%20targeting%2C%20like%20infrastructure%20or%20climate%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20depends%20on%20what%20their%20lending%20base%20is%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Cragin%20said.%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20infrastructure%2C%20you%20may%20see%20people%20coming%20from%20project%20finance%20or%20some%20of%20the%20direct%20lending%20seats%20within%20the%20banks%20or%20from%20restructuring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cead2753-a066-4b14-b5d6-c490c52c5eaa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20senior%20bankers%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20firm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20senior%20level%2C%20it%20can%20be%20harder%20to%20break%20into%20private%20credit%20from%20investment%20banking%2C%20where%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20getting%20the%20deal%20done%20versus%20thinking%20like%20an%20investor%2C%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20billion-dollar%20fund%2C%20pulling%20somebody%20at%20a%20senior%20level%20from%20a%20bank%20is%20very%20risky%2C%26quot%3B%20Judson%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20getting%20the%20deal%20done%20on%20the%20investing%20side%3B%20it's%20about%20getting%20the%20right%20deal%20done.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20smaller%20firms%2C%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20institutionalized%20firms%20will%20still%20hire%20senior%20bankers%20with%20the%20right%20experience%20because%20they%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20train%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Apollo%20CEO%20Marc%20Rowan%20recently%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20hired%20hundreds%20of%20senior%20bankers%20to%20fill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-global-management-investor-day-presentation-one-trillion-private-lending-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20growing%20credit%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20its%2016%20origination%20platforms.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20five%2C%20six%20years%2C%20we've%20taken%20300%20to%20400%20senior%20bankers%20from%20their%20job%20inside%20the%20banking%20institution%20to%20our%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Financial%20Services%20conference%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20movement%20of%20knowledge%20and%20a%20movement%20of%20relationships%20and%20a%20movement%20of%20competency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestment%20bankers%20with%20strong%20connections%20can%20also%20prove%20to%20be%20hot%20hiring%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20essentially%20bought%20those%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubinetti%20said%20of%20some%20investment%20bankers%20with%20expansive%20rolodexes%20who%20were%20poached%20by%20private-credit%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f60c5ad1-d110-412a-9830-d000c7acf709%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrivate-equity%20experience%20can%20help%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20point%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earliest%20private-credit%20firms%20were%20launched%20to%20provide%20fundraising%20to%20private-equity%20firms'%20corporate%20buyouts%2C%20creating%20a%20natural%20pathway%20from%20private%20equity%20to%20private%20credit%2C%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20private%20equity%20candidates%2C%20three-quarters%20of%20what%20they%20need%20is%20there.%20They%20think%20like%20investors%2C%20they%20understand%20how%20deals%20are%20structured%20and%20what%20they%20look%20like%2C%20and%20they%20understand%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Judson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20they%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20are%20credit%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longer%20you%20stay%20in%20private%20equity%2C%20however%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20may%20be%20to%20make%20a%20move%20since%20debt%20and%20lending%20experience%20become%20increasingly%20important%20the%20higher%20you%20get%20on%20the%20corporate%20ladder.%20Rubinetti%20said%20an%20obvious%20candidate%20might%20be%20someone%20who%20worked%20in%20private%20equity%20and%20then%20went%20to%20business%20school.%20You%20would%20need%20to%20get%20your%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20soon%20thereafter%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you're%203-4%20years%20post-MBA%2C%20it%20just%20makes%20no%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c220a9d-dea7-45c0-b952-4f55f2f8fab2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkip%20on-cycle%20recruiting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20private-credit%20shops%20will%20hire%20from%20private-equity%20firms%2C%20the%20recruiters%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20suggested%20that%20bankers%20interested%20in%20a%20private-credit%20career%20skip%20what's%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-firms-start-recruiting-early-investment-bank-apollo-kkr-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon-cycle%20recruiting.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20equity%20has%20become%20notorious%20for%20this%20recruiting%20schedule%2C%20in%20which%20they%20recruit%20junior%20investment%20bankers%20for%20jobs%20that%20won't%20start%20for%20two%20years%2C%20usually%20after%20their%20analyst%20training%20is%20complete.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20means%20that%20some%20young%20bankers%20already%20have%20their%20next%20job%20lined%20up%20before%20they%20even%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20office%20for%20their%20first%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn-cycle%20recruiting%20can%20backfire%2C%20however%2C%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20break%20into%20private%20credit%20as%20many%20private-credit%20shops%20don't%20participate%20in%20on-cycle%20recruiting%2C%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20best%20candidates%20we%20see%20for%20private%20credit%20didn't%20participate%20in%20on-cycle%20recruiting%2C%26quot%3B%20Judson%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20they%20hunkered%20down%2C%20learned%20their%20stuff%2C%20participated%2C%20put%20their%20hands%20up%2C%20and%20got%20extra%20work%2C%20which%20as%20an%20analyst%20means%20that%20they%20basically%20don't%20sleep.%20They%20then%20decide%20to%20pursue%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%20next%2C%20once%20they're%20better%20equipped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-career-pathways-junior-roles-senior-roles-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736590501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6780403488b000981b4a4696%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-career-pathways-junior-roles-senior-roles-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20signs%20point%20to%20a%20continued%20private-credit%20gold%20rush%20in%202025.%20Here%20are%20the%20top%20career%20pathways%2C%20according%20to%20recruiters%20and%20consultants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-career-pathways-junior-roles-senior-roles-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%2082-year-old%20personal%20trainer%20explains%20how%20lifting%20weights%20helped%20him%20relieve%20arthritis%20and%20joint%20paint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222235%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22an%20older%20man%20works%20out%20in%20a%20gym%20doing%20lat%20pulldown%20exercises%20on%20a%20machine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678196808951662c9f1fb7b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222981%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E82-year-old%20personal%20trainer%20Harry%20King%20said%20lifting%20weights%20helps%20strengthen%20his%20body%20so%20he%20can%20stay%20active.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Planet%20Fitness%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPersonal%20trainer%20Harry%20King%20is%2082%20and%20said%20lifting%20weights%20has%20helped%20him%20manage%20arthritis%20pain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKing%20works%20out%20five%20days%20a%20week%20doing%20bench%20presses%2C%20leg%20presses%2C%20and%20cardio%20on%20the%20elliptical.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20exercise%20allowed%20him%20to%20get%20back%20to%20an%20active%20lifestyle%20and%20makes%20everyday%20tasks%20easier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Harry%20King%20was%20in%20his%2050s%2C%20a%20doctor%20told%20him%20the%20arthritis%20in%20his%20knees%20had%20gotten%20so%20bad%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flower-your-blood-pressure-5-minutes-exercise-a-day-study-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estop%20taking%20the%20stairs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20limit%20walking%20whenever%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2082%2C%20King%20is%20not%20only%20walking%2C%20hiking%2C%20and%20working%20out%20regularly%20%E2%80%94%20he%20works%20at%20his%20local%20Planet%20Fitness%20as%20a%20personal%20trainer%2C%20leading%20others%20through%20their%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeight%20training%20is%20the%20best%20thing%20I%20can%20do%20for%20my%20arthritis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBy%20exercising%20and%20weight%20training%20I've%20built%20up%20the%20muscles%20around%20the%20knee%20to%20strengthen%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKing%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexercise-for-healthy-aging-longevity-st