nly%20ones%2C%20that%20there's%20a%20larger%20community%20that's%20all%20grieving%20the%20same%20type%20of%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220440f00f-064c-4a0b-a8dc-94b63bc42418%5C%22%3EWe're%20taking%20it%20an%20hour%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20long%20road%20ahead.%20The%20rental%20market%20is%20already%20insane.%20There%20are%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20rentals%2C%20and%20everyone's%20in%20line%20for%20the%20same%20properties.%20I'm%20sure%20there%20will%20be%20price-gouging%20and%20greedy%20people%20who%20want%20to%20get%20as%20much%20money%20as%20they%20can%20when%20they%20lease%20their%20homes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20friends%20and%20family%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20reach%20out%20and%20offer%20to%20have%20us%20stay%20with%20them.%20One%20offered%20us%20their%20condo%20in%20Sun%20Valley%20%E2%80%94%20an%20incredible%20offer%2C%20but%20uprooting%20ourselves%20feels%20like%20it'd%20be%20too%20much%20change%20so%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamily%20friends%20have%20a%20horse%20property%20in%20the%20Palisades%20and%20have%20graciously%20offered%20us%20one%20of%20their%20little%20guest%20cottages.%20We're%20waiting%20to%20see%20if%20it%20survived.%20If%20so%2C%20we'll%20go%20there%20temporarily%20because%20it's%20somewhere%20our%20daughters%20are%20familiar%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20we're%20looking%20into%20potential%20long-term%20hotel%20stay-type%20places.%20Really%2C%20we're%20just%20taking%20things%20day%20by%20day.%20We're%20booked%20at%20this%20hotel%20through%20the%20weekend%20on%20Monday%20as%20of%20now.%20We%20could%20extend%20here%2C%20but%20we%20might%20benefit%20from%20having%20a%20little%20more%20space%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wolfson's%20dog%20sleeps%20on%20the%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67819e8e8951662c9f1fbbae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%