holidays.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20years%2C%20Vail's%20rapid%20acquisitions%20and%20high%20costs%20have%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20skiers%20and%20locals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20the%20company%20grew%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20in%20skiing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20enemy%20of%20some%20ski%20bums.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20know%20just%20how%20loathed%20Vail%20Resorts%20is%2C%20just%20look%20at%20the%20lyrics%20of%20Grammy-nominated%20artist%20Noah%20Kahan's%20%26quot%3BPaul%20Revere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20place%20had%20a%20heartbeat%20in%20its%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20native%20Vermonter%20sings.%20%26quot%3BVail%20bought%20the%20mountains%2C%20and%20nothing%20was%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20look%20around%20the%20parking%20lots%20at%20the%20ski%20behemoth's%20various%20properties%2C%20which%20include%20Park%20City%2C%20Beaver%20Creek%2C%20and%20Stowe%2C%20where%20cars%20are%20frequently%20adorned%20with%20%26quot%3BVail%20Sucks%26quot%3B%20stickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGripes%20that%20the%20company%20has%20made%20skiing%20less%20accessible%20and%20more%20corporate%20were%20amplified%20this%20month%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvail-resorts-park-city-mountain-resort-ski-patrol-strike-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eski%20patrol%20strike%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20shut%20down%20much%20of%20Park%20City%2C%20causing%20chaos%20for%20vacationers%20over%20the%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20dropped%206%25%20amid%20news%20of%20the%20strike.%20But%20while%20the%20work%20stoppage%20has%20ended%2C%20the%20company's%20challenges%20are%20far%20from%20over.%20Since%20reaching%20a%20peak%20in%202021%2C%20Vail's%20share%20price%20is%20now%20down%20more%20than%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20decades%20of%20acquisitions%20and%20partnerships%2C%20Vail%20Resorts%20owns%20or%20operates%2042%20ski%20resorts%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20company%20is%20now%20facing%20decreased%20margins%20after%20a%202021%20reduction%20in%20the%20price%20of%20its%20Epic%20Pass%2C%20which%20provides%20access%20to%20Vail's%20network%20of%20mountains%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20cheap%20acquisitions%20available%2C%20Chris%20Woronka%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stock%20had%20gotten%20ahead%20of%20itself%20valuation-wise%2C%26quot%3B%20Woronka%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20days%20of%20easily%20created%20growth%20are%20kind%20of%20behind%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it's%20earned%20a%20reputation%20among%20passionate%20skiers%20as%20a%20place%20where%20crowds%20clutter%20the%20trails%20and%20lift%20lines%20and%20where%20grabbing%20a%20burger%20on%20the%20mountain%20could%20cost%20you%20%2425.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Vail%20Resorts%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20continuously%20invests%20in%20its%20properties%20to%20improve%20the%20guest%20experience%20and%20make%20skiing%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVail%20Resorts%20has%20transformed%20the%20industry%20through%20unprecedented%20investments%20in%20employees%20and%20guests%2C%20made%20the%20sport%20more%20accessible%20to%20more%20people%2C%20and%20created%20stability%20for%20our%20resorts%2C%20employees%20and%20communities%20in%20the%20face%20of%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22174a7db2-7e76-4fd9-90eb-702fa0b6df04%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20skiing%20behemoth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVail%20Resorts%20is%20the%20largest%20ski%20company%20in%20the%20world%2C%20granting%20its%20pass-holders%20unlimited%20access%20to%20dozens%20of%20resorts%20worldwide%2C%20including%20its%20upscale%20flagship%2C%20Vail%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Colorado%20Rocky%20Mountains.%20During%20its%202024%20fiscal%20year%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20July%2C%2017.6%20million%20skiers%20visited%20its%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20visitors%20pay%20big%20bucks%20for%20the%20privilege%20of%20skiing%20at%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20destinations%3A%20The%20Epic%20Pass%20had%20a%20starting%20price%20of%20%24982%20for%20the%202024-2025%20season.%20A%20lift%20ticket%20at%20Park%20City%20alone%20can%20get%20up%20to%20about%20%24300%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Vail%20Resorts%20said%20the%20company%20now%20has%20over%202%20million%20pass-holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuke%2C%20a%20former%20Vail%20Resorts%20employee%20who%20asked%20to%20go%20by%20his%20first%20name%20to%20avoid%20professional%20repercussions%2C%20told%20BI%20there%20were%20two%20main%20reasons%20Vail%20Resorts%20gets%20so%20much%20hate.%20First%2C%20it's%20buying%20up%20resorts%20at%20an%20%26quot%3Balarming%26quot%3B%20rate.%20Second%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20that%20strategy%2C%20many%20skiers%20do%20not%20believe%20the%20company%20invests%20enough%20in%20the%20quality%20and%20operations%20of%20each%20individual%20resort%2C%20instead%20relying%20on%20their%20%26quot%3Bcash%20cow%26quot%3B%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20the%20end%20game%20is%20not%20necessarily%20to%20make%20any%20one%20area%20successful%2C%20but%20to%20eventually%20own%20the%20ski%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Luke%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BSo%20then%20it's%20like%20if%20you're%20skiing%20anywhere%2C%20you're%20skiing%20Vail%26quot%3B%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJaimie%20Nichols%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20accountant%20from%20Florida%20who%20now%20lives%20in%20Denver%2C%20has%20been%20skiing%20with%20her%20family%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-places-in-united-states-to-visit-this-year-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrested%20Butte%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Colorado%2C%20since%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20when%20the%20resort%20was%20family-owned.%20She%20remembered%20lift%20tickets%20for%20kids%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20their%20age%20%E2%80%94%20%248%20for%20an%208-year-old%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20large%20base%20lodge%20where%20families%20could%20find%20affordable%20food%20options%20or%20use%20a%20microwave%20to%20heat%20up%20packed%20lunches.%20Crested%20Butte%20itself%20is%20lovingly%20called%20%26quot%3BColorado's%20Last%20Great%20Ski%20Town%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20its%20authentic%20mountain%20town%20vibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Nichols%20said%20since%20Vail%20Resorts%20acquired%20Crested%20Butte%20Ski%20Resort%20in%202018%2C%20it%20just%20hasn't%20been%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resort's%20%26quot%3Bpersona%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20completely%20different%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mueller%20family%2C%20which%20owned%20Crested%20Butte%2C%20previously%20said%20selling%20to%20Vail%20was%20a%20difficult%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20to%20look%2010%2C%2020%2C%2030%20years%20down%20the%20road%20and%20what%20that%20means%20for%20a%20small%20ski%20company%20like%20us%2C%20and%20not%20being%20as%20heavily%20financed%20like%20Vail%2C%20it's%20only%20getting%20tougher%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Erica%20Mueller%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.powder.com%2Fnews%2Fwhy-did-crested-butte-and-stevens-pass-sell-out-to-vail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPowder%3C%2Fa%3E%20magazine%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaimie%20Nichols%20and%20her%20dad%20on%20the%20mountain%20at%20Crested%20Butte.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677f17d950dfd88e193d8da3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaimie%20Nichols%20and%20her%20dad%20skiing%20Crested%20Butte.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jaimie%20Nichols%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e50487e-581a-4cdf-acbd-24d0b7a9c226%5C%22%3EWhen%20Vail%20takes%20over%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20most%20of%20Vail%20Resorts'%20properties%20are%20in%20the%20US%2C%20spanning%20from%20California%2C%20Utah%2C%20and%20Colorado%2C%20through%20Midwest%20states%20like%20Wisconsin%20and%20Michigan%2C%20and%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Northeast%20in%20Vermont%20and%20New%20Hampshire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20many%20acquisitions%20have%20turned%20the%20company%2C%20which%20was%20taken%20public%20by%20Apollo%20in%20the%201990s%20after%20the%20private%20equity%20shop%20bought%20it%20out%20of%20bankruptcy%2C%20into%20a%20financial%20behemoth%20in%20the%20hospitality%20space.%20It%20has%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20%246.7%20billion%20and%20generated%20%242.9%20billion%20in%20revenue%20and%20%24230%20million%20in%20profit%20in%20its%202024%20fiscal%20year.%20Investors%20were%20rewarded%20with%20%248.56%20in%20dividends%20per%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20complaint%20from%20skiers%20and%20snowboarders%20when%20Vail%20takes%20over%20a%20resort%20is%20a%20more%20crowded%20mountain%20and%20long%20lift%20lines.%20The%20problem%2C%20Nichols%20said%2C%20is%20that%20when%20a%20resort%20gets%20added%20to%20Vail's%20Epic%20Pass%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20destination.%20Epic%20pass-holders%20who%20previously%20wouldn't%20have%20driven%20four-plus%20hours%20from%20Denver%20to%20Crested%20Butte%20now%20make%20the%20trip%2C%20as%20do%20pass-holders%20from%20other%20states%20who%20make%20a%20vacation%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Nichols%20said%20the%20locals%20of%20the%20area%20have%20fewer%20opportunities%20to%20ski%20on%20their%20home%20mountain%2C%20and%2C%20for%20families%20who%20aren't%20season%20pass-holders%20but%20would%20like%20to%20ski%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20season%2C%20day%20passes%20get%20too%20expensive%20and%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20problems%20are%20compounded%20by%20factors%20that%20are%20affecting%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-housing-crisis-us-west-coast-cause-explained-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etowns%20in%20the%20West%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20don't%20even%20have%20a%20ski%20resort%3A%20an%20increase%20in%20short-term%20rentals%20and%20transplants%20from%20cities%20moving%20to%20small%20towns%20in%20the%20age%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20contributed%20to%20higher%20home%20prices%20and%20costs%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVail%20has%20said%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20reinvesting%20in%20the%20resorts%20it%20acquires%2C%20estimating%20its%20capital%20investments%20in%20the%202024%20fiscal%20year%20to%20be%20between%20%24189%20million%20to%20%24194%20million.%20For%20instance%2C%20at%20Whistler%20Blackcomb%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20replacing%20a%20four-person%20lift%20with%20a%20six-person%20high-speed%20lift.%20At%20Park%20City%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20replacing%20a%20lift%20with%20a%2010-person%20gondola.%20It%20also%20said%20it%20planned%20to%20invest%20in%20snowmaking%20capabilities%20at%20Park%20City%20and%20Hunter%20Mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Vail%20Resorts%20said%20the%20Epic%20Pass%20has%20also%20added%20stability%20to%20an%20industry%20that%20was%20previously%20%26quot%3Bruled%20by%20weather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20means%20in%20a%20good%20snow%20year%2C%20the%20industry%20would%20prosper%2C%20but%20in%20a%20year%20with%20low%20snow%2C%20skiers%20and%20snowboarders%20would%20opt%20not%20to%20visit%2C%20and%20ski%20resorts%20would%20suffer%2C%20along%20with%20the%20employees%20who%20worked%20there%20and%20the%20surrounding%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20meant%20that%20resorts%20couldn't%20predict%20their%20business%20%E2%80%94%20thus%20were%20not%20investing%20in%20infrastructure%20or%20their%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vail%20introduced%20the%20Epic%20Pass%20in%202008%2C%20it%20was%20cheaper%20than%20many%20season%20passes%20offered%20at%20individual%20resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20the%20company's%20Epic%20Day%20Passes%2C%20which%20offer%20more%20flexibility%20than%20traditional%20lift%20tickets%2C%20are%20significantly%20discounted%20if%20they%20are%20purchased%20before%20the%20season%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20incentivizing%20guests%20to%20buy%20their%20skiing%20and%20riding%20ahead%20of%20the%20season%2C%20we%20lock%20in%20revenue%20before%20the%20snow%20falls%2C%20which%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20continually%20invest%20back%20into%20our%20resorts%2C%20our%20employees%2C%20and%20our%20communities%2C%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20weather%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overview%20of%20Vail%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677f175ff83fcec7e5b526fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVail%20Resorts%20has%20more%20than%2040%20ski%20resorts%20worldwide%2C%20including%20its%20namesake%20flagship%20in%20Colorado.%3Cp%3EAdventure_Photo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e09d1b3-992a-4a7c-bf51-a5c348eafaf0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20Vail%20critics%20still%20buy%20Epic%20Passes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20biggest%20competitor%20is%20Alterra%20Mountain%20Company%2C%20which%20owns%20mountains%20like%20Steamboat%20and%20Deer%20Valley%20and%20is%20owned%20by%20private%20equity%20shop%20KSL%20and%20investment%20firm%20Henry%20Crown.%20Alterra%20runs%20the%20Ikon%20Pass%2C%20which%20is%20even%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20Epic%20Pass%2C%20starting%20at%20%241%2C249.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Epic%20and%20Ikon%20passes'%20value%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20one%20uses%20them.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20good%20deal%20for%20folks%20who%20ski%20frequently%20and%20would%20like%20to%20visit%20different%20mountains%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20argument%20the%20companies%20use%20when%20they%20increase%20the%20pricing%20on%20nearly%20everything%20else%2C%20including%20day%20passes%2C%20ski%20school%2C%20rentals%2C%20and%20on-mountain%20dining%20and%20amenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20offering%20a%20good%20deal%20with%20the%20Epic%20Pass%2C%20Woronka%2C%20the%20Deutsche%20Bank%20analyst%2C%20said%20Vail%20also%20still%20has%20a%20strong%20brand%20name%20going%20for%20it%20and%20great%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20really%20terrific%20mountains.%20It's%20some%20of%20the%20best%20terrain%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20this%20big%2C%20nice%2C%20wide%20portfolio%20across%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%2C%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20cater%20to%20everyone%20and%20do%20it%20profitably%20can%20be%20a%20difficult%20proposition%2C%26quot%3B%20Woronka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20luxury%20experience%20that%20Vail%20is%20selling%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20crowds%20on%20the%20mountain%20can%20make%20the%20guests%20feel%20a%20little%20less%20special%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Vail's%20dominance%20means%20that%20many%20who%20complain%20about%20the%20company%20still%20buy%20Epic%20Passes.%20It%20often%20makes%20the%20most%20financial%20sense%20for%20those%20who%20plan%20to%20ski%20most%20weekends%2C%20and%20if%20all%20their%20friends%20are%20doing%20the%20Epic%20Pass%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuke%2C%20the%20former%20Vail%20employee%2C%20said%20running%20a%20ski%20operation%20is%20costly%20and%20complicated.%20And%2C%20he%20added%2C%20there's%20no%20denying%20that%20some%20of%20the%20resorts%20bought%20up%20by%20Vail%20may%20not%20have%20survived%20otherwise.%20But%20he%20said%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20that%20is%20the%20relatively%20low%20cost%20of%20the%20Epic%20Pass%20has%20drawn%20many%20away%20from%20their%20local%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20mountains%20wouldn't%20have%20survived%2C%26quot%3B%20Luke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20said%20he%20thinks%20having%20to%20compete%20with%20a%20large%20company%20like%20Vail%20is%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20some%20family-run%20resorts%20were%20struggling%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvail-resorts-biggest-hated-name-skiing-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736589901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677edcde50dfd88e193d7f83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvail-resorts-biggest-hated-name-skiing-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vail%20Resorts%2C%20which%20faced%20backlash%20over%20a%20Park%20City%20ski%20patrol%20strike%2C%20gets%20hate%20from%20locals%20and%20ski%20bums%20over%20the%20corporatization%20of%20skiing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis%2CMadeline%20Berg%2CKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvail-resorts-biggest-hated-name-skiing-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Communalism%20behind%20attacks%20on%20minorities%3F%20What%20B'desh%20police%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736589739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117145746%2Cimgsize-1419165.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmajority-of-attacks-on-minorities-in-bangladesh-not-communally-motivated-but-political-in-nature-police-report%2Farticleshow%2F117144745.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20police%20report%20states%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20since%20August%202024%20were%20politically%20motivated.%20With%201%2C769%20