%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicro-trends%20that%20circulate%20on%20social%20media%20can%20trigger%20some%20to%20make%20too%20many%20online%20purchases.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuy-now-pay-later%20can%20make%20the%20true%20costs%20of%20buying%20items%20seem%20lower.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20payments%20add%20up%20over%20time%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20debt%20spiral%20that's%20difficult%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-loans%2Fwhat-is-buy-now-pay-later%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuy-now-pay-later%20services%20(BNPL)%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20Klarna%20and%20Affirm%2C%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20influencer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-micro-trends-cause-financial-problems-fashion-mental-health-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicro-trends%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20but%20young%20people%20say%20such%20services%20are%20increasingly%20trapping%20them%20into%20a%20vicious%20debt%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJess%20Riley%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20content%20creator%20who%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40jess.riley_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20her%20debt%20journey%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20BNPL%2C%20combined%20with%20micro-fashion%20trends%2C%20almost%20led%20her%20to%20financial%20ruin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20definitely%20one%20of%20those%20people%20that%20was%20very%20susceptible%20to%20influencers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20someone%20put%20out%20a%20new%20necklace%2C%20I%20instantly%20wanted%20that%20necklace%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20would%20put%20it%20on%20Klarna%20just%20so%20I%20could%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20impulse%20buying%20was%20just%20that%2C%20though.%20Sometimes%20Riley%20would%20forget%20what%20she%20ordered%20almost%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20is%20far%20from%20alone.%20Consumers%20and%20commentators%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20say%20BNPL%20tempts%20people%20to%20make%20impulsive%20purchases%20and%20rack%20up%20debt%20by%20making%20it%20seem%20like%20costs%20are%20less%20than%20they%20actually%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20shopping%20online%20so%20easy%20that%20it%20almost%20becomes%20mindless%2C%20particularly%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimon%20Trevethick%2C%20head%20of%20communications%20at%20StepChange%2C%20a%20UK%20debt%20charity%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20regulation%20of%20BNPL%20apps%20means%20people%20can%20accumulate%20multiple%20debts%20across%20various%20providers%20%26quot%3Boften%20without%20proper%20affordability%20assessments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20repayments%20become%20unaffordable%2C%20these%20debts%20can%20then%20incur%20late%20fees%20and%20interest%20charges%20that%20place%20people%20in%20financial%20difficulty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20took%20steps%20last%20year%20to%20increase%20regulation%20of%20BNPL%20providers%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3EReuters%20reported%3Cspan%3E.%20Lenders%20will%20be%20required%20to%20refund%20returned%20products%2C%20and%20provide%20assistance%20with%20billing%20disputes.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20not%20required%20to%20assess%20whether%20a%20customer%20can%20afford%20the%20loan%20and%20repayments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1f12dd6-bfd6-4729-a0dc-b28e62564e86%5C%22%3EThe%20affordability%20illusion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20amount%20owed%20to%20BNPL%20services%20is%20unknown%2C%20but%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20the%20number%20of%20such%20loans%20in%20the%20US%20increased%20by%201%2C100%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CFPB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20holiday%20season%2C%20Americans%20were%20expected%20to%20spend%20%2418.5%20billion%20using%20BNPL%20services%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20your%20purchase%20today%2C%20you%20can%20explain%20away%20not%20having%20the%20money%20by%20making%20multiple%20payments%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Traci%20Williams%2C%20a%20certified%20clinical%20psychologist%20and%20financial%20therapist%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20what%20you%20don't%20consider%20is%20that%20not%20being%20able%20to%20afford%20it%20today%20likely%20means%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20you%20cannot%20afford%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToni-Ann%2C%20who%20posts%20content%20on%20TikTok%20about%20paying%20off%20her%20debt%20under%20the%20handle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40financeaccountingdiaries%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40financeaccountingdiaries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20social%20media%2C%20with%20the%20power%20of%20influencers%20and%20algorithms%2C%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20the%20debt%20spiral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20pressures%20you%20to%20want%20to%20buy%20what%20everybody%20else%20has%20got%20or%20whatever%20you%20keep%20seeing%20advertised.%20Then%20Klarna%20is%20an%20option%2C%20so%20you're%20just%20like%2C%20'oh%2C%20I%20just%20can%20spread%20the%20payments'%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20services%20make%20it%20feel%20like%20you%20only%20owe%20a%20small%20amount%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20sums%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeth%20Fuller%20shared%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40bethmfuller%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20story%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20she%20has%20reduced%20her%20%248%2C000%20of%20credit%20card%20debt%20to%20almost%20nothing%20by%20cutting%20back%20on%20needless%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fiframely.net%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20data-iframely-url%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fiframely.net%2FRiVayp2%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40bethmfuller%2Fphoto%2F7457539334812618016%3Fis_from_webapp%3D1%26sender_device%3Dpc%26web_id%3D7407717715684869664%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFuller%20told%20BI%20she%20felt%20the%20pressure%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20fashion%20she%20saw%20influencers%20share%20on%20social%20media.%20She%20said%20she%20realized%20that%20once%20she'd%20bought%20something%2C%20her%20brain%20would%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20were%20feeling%20outdated%20so%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20surely%20I%20can't%20need%20more%20stuff.%20But%20an%20event%20would%20come%20around%2C%20and%20I%20just%20wouldn't%20feel%20on%20trend%20for%20the%20event%2C%20even%20though%20I'd%20bought%20clothes%20last%20month.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225330a6f9-957a-4231-886d-0cc37887afdb%5C%22%3ECurbing%20the%20habit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20typically%20don't%20like%20waiting%20to%20buy%20things%2C%20Williams%20told%20BI%2C%20which%20makes%20BNPL%20so%20tempting.%20It%20also%20hurts%20less%20to%20stretch%20the%20payments%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20pain%20receptors%20in%20the%20brain%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20activated%20by%20larger%20purchases%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMentally%2C%20it%20seems%20easier%20to%20pay%20small%20amounts%20over%20time%20than%20in%20one%20lump%20sum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20recommended%20asking%20yourself%20if%20the%20purchase%20is%20something%20you%20want%20or%20need%20and%20then%20considering%20saving%20up%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20outright%3A%20%26quot%3BFocus%20on%20stopping%20the%20bleeding%20by%20no%20longer%20using%20these%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Klarna%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20offers%20%26quot%3Ba%20fairer%20and%20more%20sustainable%20alternative%26quot%3B%20to%20traditional%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20conduct%20strict%20eligibility%20checks%20on%20each%20purchase%20using%20real-time%20data%2C%20constantly%20reassess%20our%20lending%20criteria%20and%20spending%20limits%20to%20ensure%20we%20only%20lend%20to%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20to%20repay%2C%20and%20we%20restrict%20the%20use%20of%20our%20services%20after%20missed%20payments%20to%20stop%20debt%20accumulating%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Afterpay%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20it%20did%20not%20conduct%20hard%20inquiries%20or%20report%20account%20activity%20to%20credit%20bureaus.%20They%20said%20the%20company%20also%20capped%20late-payment%20fees%20at%2025%25%20of%20the%20order%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20are%20offered%20small%20spending%20limits%20when%20they%20first%20join%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20and%2095%25%20of%20installments%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202024%20were%20paid%20on%20time%2C%20and%2098%25%20incurred%20no%20late%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225180d3be-8db4-4993-b120-d170f6e43799%5C%22%3EGetting%20out%20of%20the%20hole%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Affirm%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20there%20were%20no%20late%20fees%20or%20hidden%20charges%2C%20and%20if%20a%20customer%20did%20not%20repay%20their%20loan%2C%20they%20could%20no%20longer%20use%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20influencers%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20BNPL%20helped%20maintain%20their%20shopping%20addictions.%20Toni-Ann%20has%20almost%20paid%20off%20all%20her%20debt.%20She%20said%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20hole%2C%20but%20it%20started%20with%20changing%20her%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20spoke%20to%20BI%20last%20year%2C%20Riley%20only%20owed%20another%20%24800%20and%20expected%20to%20be%20debt-free%20within%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20relapsed%20and%20used%20BNPL%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20but%20doesn't%20beat%20herself%20up%20about%20it.%20Overall%2C%20she's%20mostly%20changed%20the%20way%20she%20thinks%20about%20spending%20and%20doesn't%20let%20herself%20be%20tempted%20by%20the%20micro-trends%20influencers%20are%20promoting%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20marathon%2C%20not%20a%20sprint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJyoti%20Mann%20contributed%20reporting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-now-pay-later-apps-spending-debt-spiral-influencers-alarm-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736588882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6781502150dfd88e193dd38f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-now-pay-later-apps-spending-debt-spiral-influencers-alarm-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Content%20creator%20Jess%20Riley%20has%20shared%20her%20debt%20journey%20on%20TikTok%20and%20says%20BNPL%2C%20combined%20with%20micro-fashion%20trends%2C%20almost%20led%20her%20to%20financial%20ruin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40businessinsider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-now-pay-later-apps-spending-debt-spiral-influencers-alarm-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Imran%20Khan%20approaches%20Lahore%20high%20court%20for%20bail%20in%20May%209%20cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736588495000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117145208%2Cimgsize-627636.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-imran-khan-approaches-lahore-high-court-for-bail-in-may-9-cases%2Farticleshow%2F117145142.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117145142.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2