20to%20replace%20Internet%20Explorer%2C%20and%20runs%20faster%20and%20with%20more%20features.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEdge%20now%20works%20with%20Microsoft's%20new%20AI-powered%20features%20like%20Copilot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20once%20an%20old%20joke%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-windows-pc-vs-apple-mac-os-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWindows%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%3A%20%26quot%3BInternet%20Explorer%20is%20the%20best%20browser%20to%20download%20a%20better%20browser%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Internet%20Explorer%20%E2%80%94%20Microsoft's%20old%20flagship%20internet%20browser%20%E2%80%94%20was%20been%20around%20for%20years%2C%20and%20few%20people%20actually%20liked%20it.%20That's%20a%20big%20reason%20why%20in%202015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-mustafa-suleyman-ai-copilot-update-reviews-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20Edge%2C%20their%20new%20and%20improved%20browser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20gradually%20replaced%20Internet%20Explorer%20and%20became%20increasingly%20popular%20over%20the%20years%2C%20until%20the%20latter%20browser%20finally%20shuttered%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Edge%20was%20created%20with%20the%20Windows%20user%20in%20mind%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-ios%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%20can%20download%20it%20on%20their%20Macs%2C%20iPhones%2C%20or%20iPads%2C%20too.%20Edge%20can%20even%20be%20used%20on%20Linux%20and%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-xbox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EXbox%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20made%20a%20big%20effort%20with%20Edge%20to%20improve%20the%20browsing%20experience%2C%20and%20it's%20paid%20off.%20Microsoft%20Edge%20has%20enough%20features%20and%20benefits%20that%20it's%20actually%20a