C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20page%20should%20automatically%20detect%20whether%20you're%20using%20a%20Mac%2C%20PC%2C%20iPhone%2C%20or%20Android%20device.%20If%20you%20think%20the%20page%20has%20gotten%20it%20wrong%2C%20click%20the%20arrow%20next%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BDownload%26quot%3B%20button%20to%20see%20all%20the%20available%20versions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-edge%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736588102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677308e79de00e389eb3de93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-edge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Microsoft%20Edge%20is%20the%20internet%20browser%20Microsoft%20created%20for%20Windows%20devices%20to%20replace%20Internet%20Explorer.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ross%20James%2CMichelle%20Mark)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-edge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Attacks%20AAP%20Over%20'CAG%20Report'%20On%20Liquor%20Policy%20Case%2C%20Party%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20today%20escalated%20its%20attack%20on%20AAP%20following%20findings%20from%20a%20leaked%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20report%20regarding%20the%20city's%20controversial%20excise%20policy.%20Questioning%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20report%2C%20AAP%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20asked%20whether%20the%20alleged%20findings%20were%20made%20at%20the%20BJP%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20which%20allegedly%20outlines%20major%20lapses%20and%20violations%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20fresh%20row%20ahead%20of%20the%20February%205%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20has%20not%20been%20officially%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purported%20CAG%20report%2C%20parts%20of%20which%20have%20reached%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20alleges%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20Excise%20Policy%20caused%20a%20loss%20of%20over%20Rs%202%2C026%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20including%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%20890%20crore%20due%20to%20the%20failure%20to%20re-tender%20surrendered%20retail%20liquor%20licenses.%20An%20additional%20loss%20of%20Rs%20941%20crore%20allegedly%20stemmed%20from%20exemptions%20granted%20to%20zonal%20licensees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20approvals%20from%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(LG)%2C%20the%20Cabinet%2C%20and%20the%20Assembly%20were%20allegedly%20bypassed.%20The%20report%20further%20claims%20that%20the%20Group%20of%20Ministers%20(GoM)%20led%20by%20Manish%20Sisodia%20ignored%20recommendations%20from%20an%20expert%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20seized%20on%20the%20alleged%20findings%2C%20accusing%20the%20AAP%20government%20of%20gross%20corruption%20and%20mismanagement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20their%20(AAP)%20policies%20were%20so%20good%20then%20why%20were%20they%20taken%20aback%3F%20Today%20AAP%20has%20no%20answer%20to%20Delhi's%20broken%20roads%2C%20dirty%20water%20in%20homes%2C%20rising%20electricity%20bills%2C%20mountains%20of%20garbage%20and%20pollution.%20Today%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20want%20to%20be%20free%20from%20'AAP-da'%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20leader%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20questioned%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20purported%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20is%20the%20CAG%20report%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20a%20copy%3F%20Is%20it%20made%20at%20the%20BJP%20office%3F%20The%20BJP%20is%20scared.%20They%20have%20become%20mentally%20unstable.%20We%20cannot%20res