g-unjustified-tariff-threats-from-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F117143605.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcanadas-fm-melanie-joly-opts-out-of-liberal-leadership-race-citing-unjustified-tariff-threats-from-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F117143605.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20Officials%20Would%20'Scream'%2C%20'Curse'%20At%20Meta%20Team%20To%20Take%20Down%20Content%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20CEO%20of%20Meta%2C%20recently%20shared%20an%20account%20of%20Biden%20administration%20officials%20berating%20Facebook%20staff%20over%20content%20removal%20requests.%20On%20%26quot%3BThe%20Joe%20Rogan%20Experience%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20Zuckerberg%20recounted%2C%20%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20these%20people%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration%20would%20call%20up%20our%20team%20and%2C%20like%2C%20scream%20at%20them%20and%20curse.%26quot%3B%20He%20emphasised%20that%20Facebook%20eventually%20pushed%20back%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20got%20to%20this%20point%20where%20we%20were%20like%2C%20'No%2C%20we're%20not%20gonna%2C%20we're%20not%20gonna%20take%20down%20things%20that%20are%20true.%20That's%20ridiculous.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Zuckerberg%20has%20spoken%20out%20about%20administration%20pressure.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Rep.%20Jim%20Jordan%20last%20year%2C%20Zuckerberg%20stated%20that%20the%20White%20House%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%20pressured%26quot%3B%20Facebook%20to%20remove%20specific%20COVID-19%20content%2C%20including%20humor%20and%20satire.%20Zuckerberg%20admitted%20that%20Facebook%20complied%20at%20times%20but%20suggested%20they%20would%20make%20different%20decisions%20in%20the%20future.%20He%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20made%20some%20choices%20that%2C%20with%20the%20benefit%20of%20hindsight%20and%20new%20information%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20make%20today%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20want%20us%20to%20like%20him%20the%20way%20we%20like%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20%2C%20so%20he's%20on%20Joe%20Rogan%20saying%20things%20we%20like%20to%20hear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fv8BrecoeT6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fv8BrecoeT6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Winnie%20Schola%20(%40WinnieSchola)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWinnieSchola%2Fstatus%2F1877790554005582216%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2010%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20responded%20at%20the%20time%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20confronted%20with%20a%20deadly%20pandemic%2C%20this%20Administration%20encouraged%20responsible%20actions%20to%20protect%20public%20health%20and%20safety.%26quot%3B%20They%20emphasised%20their%20position%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20tech%20companies%20and%20other%20private%20actors%20should%20take%20into%20account%20the%20effects%20their%20actions%20have%20on%20the%20American%20people%2C%20while%20making%20independent%20choices%20about%20the%20information%20they%20present%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20shared%20a%20specific%20example%20of%20the%20administration's%20requests%2C%20involving%20a%20meme%20featuring%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20pointing%20at%20a%20TV%20screen%20advertising%20a%20class%20action%20lawsuit%20for%20people%20who%20took%20the%20Covid%20vaccine.%20Zuckerberg%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20like%2C%20'No%2C%20you%20have%20to%20take%20that%20down%2C'%26quot%3B%20but%20Facebook%20refused%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20gonna%20take%20down%20humor%20and%20satire.%20We're%20not%20gonna%20take%20down%20things%20that%20are%2C%20that%20are%20true%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20case%20that%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202023.%20The%20plaintiffs%20sought%20to%20bar%20government%20officials%20from%20communicating%20with%20social%20media%20companies%2C%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ultimately%20threw%20out%20the%20lawsuit%20in%20a%206-3%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZuckerberg's%20comments%20come%20as%20Meta%20announces%20changes%20to%20its%20content%20moderation%20policies.%20They%20have%20announced%20an%20end%20to%20their%20fact-checking%20program%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20a%20community-driven%20structure.%20Additionally%2C%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20will%20relax%20rules%20related%20to%20political%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20notable%20to%20mention%20that%20he%20is%20one%20of%20the%20tech%20moguls%20whose%20company%20has%20pledged%20to%20donate%20%241%20million%20to%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20inaugural%20fund.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736584500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Faaanmjqg_mark-zuckerberg-afp_625x300_11_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-officials-would-scream-curse-at-meta-team-to-take-down-content-7449361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20CEO%20of%20Meta%2C%20recently%20shared%20a%20shocking%20account%20of%20Biden%20administration%20officials%20berating%20Facebook%20staff%20over%20content%20removal%20requests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-officials-would-scream-curse-at-meta-team-to-take-down-content-7449361%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20been%20wearing%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20to%20track%20my%20fitness%20for%204%20years.%20Here%20are%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20the%20device%20loved%20by%20celebs%20and%20business%20execs.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Rachel%20Hosie%20on%20a%20walk%20in%20sports%20kit%2C%20and%20with%20a%20glass%20of%20Champagne.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%2