-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOura%204%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plus%20a%20%245.99-a-month%20subscription%2C%20it's%20not%20cheap%2C%20but%20neither%20is%20an%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20which%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%24799%20for%20the%20top%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20were%20always%20surprised%20when%20I%20told%20them%20my%20ring%20was%20an%20activity%20tracker.%20Now%20everyone%20from%20the%20saleswoman%20at%20a%20jewelry%20counter%20to%20my%20sports%20teammates%20ask%20me%20if%20I'm%20wearing%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20and%20what%20it's%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20that%20I've%20found%20after%20four%20years%20of%20wearing%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oura%20ring%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a94f5743bb77284b9e1a7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225556%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Oura%20Ring%20shows%20all%20the%20data%20it%20collects%20on%20the%20app.%3Cp%3EOura%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7ffc01e-a25e-496d-948e-0bfe5ebb84ea%5C%22%3ECon%3A%20You%20can't%20really%20wear%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20while%20weightlifting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20look%20of%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20is%20a%20big%20selling%20point%20to%20me%2C%20a%20wrist%20strap%20would%20be%20better%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-5-years-lifting-weights-exercise-fat-loss-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20the%20bread%20and%20butter%20of%20my%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20movements%20like%20deadlifts%20and%20pull-ups%2C%20I%20take%20my%20ring%20off%20as%20it%20pinches%20my%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I'm%20only%20interested%20in%20tracking%20the%20weights%20I%20use%20and%20reps%20in%20workouts%2C%20which%20trackers%20can't%20do%20and%20so%20I%20log%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fbf4fda-fcab-49df-9a6b-6e1a26900efb%5C%22%3EPro%3A%20The%20Oura%20Ring%20tracks%20my%20daily%20movements%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20that%20my%20Oura%20Ring%20picks%20up%20all%20my%20movement%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20including%20my%20steps%20(a%20metric%20the%20Whoop%20strap%2C%20for%20example%2C%20doesn't%20track).%20And%20it's%20perfectly%20comfortable%20to%20wear%2C%20say%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-weightlifter-made-running-habit-hybrid-training-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20a%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20when%20I%20like%20to%20know%20my%20heart%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oura%20Ring%20can%20track%20various%20activities%2C%20and%20it's%20remarkably%20good%20at%20knowing%20what%20you've%20done%2C%20from%20cycling%20to%20rowing.%20It%20even%20picks%20up%20housework%20as%20an%20activity%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20a%20fantastic%20way%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20all%20daily%20movement%2C%20not%20just%20formal%20exercise%2C%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20picks%20up%20restful%20moments%2C%20including%20naps%20if%20I%20were%20much%20of%20a%20napper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20ring's%20battery%20life%20has%20slightly%20worsened%20with%20time%2C%20I%20only%20have%20to%20charge%20it%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20every%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20people%20like%20having%20a%20screen%20on%20their%20device%2C%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20is%20shown%20on%20an%20app.%20I%20like%20being%20able%20to%20check%20mine%20when%20it%20suits%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222117%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Aniston%20wearing%20an%20Oura%20Ring%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677fd849f83fcec7e5b52f6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Aniston%20has%20been%20spotted%20wearing%20an%20Oura%20Ring.%3Cp%3EJames%20Devaney%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ce65752-f155-4ac5-859d-a975c365db21%5C%22%3EPro%3A%20Oura%20Rings%20provide%20detailed%20sleep%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOura%20Rings%20are%20generally%20considered%20to%20be%20among%20the%20most%20accurate%20wearables%20for%20tracking%20sleep%2C%20and%20it's%20really%20interesting%20to%20see%20not%20just%20how%20long%20I've%20slept%20in%20total%20but%20also%20the%20split%20between%20sleep%20phases%2C%20how%20long%20it%20took%20me%20to%20fall%20asleep%2C%20and%20the%20overall%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2Farticle%2F10.1088%2F1361-6579%2Fab840a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20University%20of%20Oulu%20in%20Finland%20found%20that%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20measures%20resting%20heart%20rate%20at%2099.9%25%20reliability%20compared%20to%20a%20medical-grade%20electrocardiogram.%20Oura%20supported%20the%20study%20by%20providing%20equipment%20and%20software%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20authors%20were%20employed%20by%20Oura.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20study's%20design%20or%20collection%20and%20analysis%20of%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20waking%20up%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20reaching%20for%20the%20Oura%20app%20to%20see%20how%20I%20slept%2C%20rather%20than%20checking%20in%20with%20my%20body%20and%20seeing%20how%20I%20actually%20feel%2C%20which%20I%20don't%20think%20is%20a%20great%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sleep%20data%20is%20clever%20and%20interesting%2C%20but%20arguably%20unnecessary%20for%20the%20average%20person.%20Wearing%20a%20smart%20ring%20won't%20improve%20your%20sleep%2C%20but%20it%20can%20help%20you%20change%20your%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220d599c8-e1ff-4eac-8f45-075fdc6bce6d%5C%22%3EPro%3A%20The%20Oura%20Ring%20encourages%20you%20to%20rest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Hosie%20taking%20a%20mirror%20selfie%20wearing%20a%20pink%20floral%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6781242350dfd88e193dc843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Hosie%20likes%20being%20able%20to%20wear%20her%20Oura%20Ring%20with%20any%20outfit.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Whoop%20strap%2C%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20smart%20devices%20not%20just%20to%20push%20people%20to%20move%20more%20but%20to%20help%20users%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-fitness-culture-shifted-focus-on-recovery-trackers-promote-balance-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebalance%20recovery%20with%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you're%20not%20well%20rested%2C%20Oura%20will%20suggest%20taking%20it%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20that%20it%20promotes%20balance%2C%20but%20most%20people%20can%20only%20exercise%20at%20certain%20times%20and%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20waiting%20for%20the%20next%20day%20when%20their%20Oura%20Ring%20might%20say%20they're%20in%20a%20better%20place%20to%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20it's%20no%20bad%20thing%20to%20factor%20in%20that%20perhaps%20you%20should%20do%20a%20slightly%20lighter%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220369789b-4a38-447a-b6f5-c081927fa43f%5C%22%3EPro%3A%20The%20temperature%20sensors%20can%20tell%20you%20if%20you're%20sick%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOura%20Rings%20are%20very%20sensitive%20to%20body%20temperature%2C%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20methods%20they%20use%20to%20determine%20when%20you're%20feeling%20tired%20and%20where%20you%20are%20in%20your%20menstrual%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20features%20are%20really%20smart%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20heard%20various%20Oura%20users%20say%20their%20rings%20know%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20ill%20before%20they%20do%2C%20and%20studies%20support%20this.%20Similarly%2C%20mine%20has%20alerted%20me%20when%20my%20period%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20few%20days%20late%20based%20on%20my%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1d3cfa6-640c-4f09-bd68-97ee08b7a339%5C%22%3EI%20take%20Oura%20Ring%20data%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20do%20believe%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20accurate%20wearables%20available%2C%20I%20also%20know%20to%20take%20all%20the%20data%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%2C%20and%20I%20won't%20live%20or%20die%20by%20what%20it%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ffitness-wearables-trackers-pros-cons-wellness-experts-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELivvy%20Probert%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20personal%20trainer%2C%20sports%20scientist%2C%20and%20head%20of%20science%20at%20personal%20health%20assessment%20company%20Hawq%20Score%2C%20previously%20told%20me.%20Wearable%20tech%20like%20Oura%20Rings%20are%20great%20for%20monitoring%20your%20own%20sleep%20and%20activity%20trends%20and%20progress%2C%20but%20because%20accuracy%20can't%20be%20guaranteed%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20necessarily%20read%20too%20much%20into%20the%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foura-ring-fitness-tracker-pros-cons-after-years-wearing-style-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736584381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677fd705f83fcec7e5b52f34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foura-ring-fitness-tracker-pros-cons-after-years-wearing-style-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20wearing%20an%20Oura%20Ring%20for%20four%20years%2C%20fitness%20reporter%20Rachel%20Hosie%20said%20she%20loves%20that%20it's%20stylish%20and%20discreet%2C%20and%20tracks%20a%20range%20of%20health%20data.%22%2