20BJP%20and%20Sena%20parting%20ways%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20estranged%20cousin%20Raj%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navanirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%2C%20became%20closer%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20meeting%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20during%20the%20Winter%20Session%20of%20the%20Assembly%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20he%20had%20asserted%20he%20won't%20indulge%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20revenge%20and%20that%20all%20leaders%20had%20responded%20positively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sharad%20Pawar%20Is%20Intelligent'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20also%20spoke%20about%20veteran%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20praises%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20after%20the%20election%20results.%20He%20said%20Mr%20Pawar%20has%20realised%20how%20the%20RSS%20overcame%20the%20fake%20narrative%20spread%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20many%20people%20inspired%20by%20the%20RSS%20played%20their%20role%20and%20burst%20the%20fake%20narrative.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20saheb%20is%20very%20intelligent.%20He%20would%20have%20studied%20this%20and%20realised%20that%20this%20(RSS)%20is%20not%20a%20regular%20political%20power%20but%20a%20nationalist%20power.%20That%20is%20why%20he%20may%20have%20praised%20the%20RSS%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20good%20to%20praise%20others%20in%20a%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20chances%20of%20Mr%20Pawar's%20faction%20reuniting%20with%20the%20original%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20the%20developments%20between%202019%20and%202024%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20anything%20can%20happen.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20goes%20to%20another%20party%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20comes%20to%20us.%20Anything%20can%20happen%20in%20politics%20but%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20should%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20Late%20Vilasji%20Fadnis%20Jivhala%20programme%20in%20Nagpu