p%3EEveryone%20should%20want%20to%20have%2090-hour%20work%20weeks%20(roughly%2012.5%20hours%20per%20day%2C%20if%20working%20seven%20days%20a%20week)%20for%20the%20nation.%20It's%20absolutely%20not%20as%20if%20these%20CEOs%20are%20looking%20to%20increase%20their%20own%20profits.%20CEOs%20are%20so%20massively%20underpaid%20anyway.%20That's%20another%20universally%20acknowledged%20truth.%20There%20isn't%20an%20ounce%20of%20selfish%20interest%20here.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20here%20are%20seven%20ways%20to%20utilise%20your%20Sundays%20to%20be%20your%20best%20productive%20self.%20Before%20we%20begin%2C%20remember%2C%20the%20kids%20will%20try%20to%20misguide%20you%20into%20believing%20that%20humans%20deserve%20rest%20and%20relaxation.%20They%20will%20cite%20four-day%20workweeks%20in%20Japan%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98right%20to%20disconnect'%20in%20France%2C%20where%20employers%20legally%20cannot%20trouble%20employees%20after%20work%20hours.%20But%2C%20don't%20get%20swayed.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20productive%20every%20second%20of%20your%20life%2C%20till%20the%20day%20you%20die.%20You're%20letting%20down%20humanity%20every%20moment%20you%20spend%20on%20rest%2C%20relaxation%2C%20family%2C%20hobbies%2C%20or%20(gasp)%20staring%20at%20your%20husband%2Fwife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Productive%20Visual%20Activities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20film%20and%20TV%20industry%20works%20ceaselessly.%20No%20Sundays%20or%20Diwali%20or%20New%20Year%20for%20them.%20Writers%20write%20day%20and%20night%2C%20crews%20shoot%20for%20months%2C%20singers%2C%20actors%2C%20stunt%20artists%2C%20editors%2C%20and%20set%20staff%2C%20all%20slave%20it%20out%20for%20months.%20To%20support%20their%20hard%20work%2C%20you%20must%2C%20as%20a%20responsible%20citizen%2C%20binge-watch%20something%20on%20Sundays.%20Important%3A%20involve%20your%20husband%2Fwife%20as%20well%2C%20so%20they%20are%20not%20doing%20any%20unproductive%20staring%20at%20you.%20Do%20it%20for%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Productive%20Social%20Work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMan%20is%20a%20social%20animal.%20Sorry%2C%20that%20was%20too%20gendered.%20Humans%20are%20social%20animals.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20as%20productive%20humans%20to%20give%20back%20to%20our%20fellow%20humans.%20Take%20your%20friends%20to%20a%20local%20watering%20hole%2C%20indulge%20in%20local%20drinks%20and%20food%2C%20ensure%20local%20businesses%20thrive%2C%20and%20play%20your%20role%20in%20improving%20our%20economy.%20After%20a%20fun%20evening%20of%20rest%2C%20relaxation%20and%20inebriation%2C%20most%20people%20will%20forget%20about%20all%20their%20problems%20at%20work%20and%20return%20to%20work%20on%20Monday%20for%20a%2014-hour%20shift%20voluntarily.%20Take%20your%20husband%2Fwife%20along%20as%20well%20but%20ensure%20they're%20not%20staring%20at%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Productive%20Physical%20Activity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20one%20is%20obvious%3B%20unless%20you%20are%20in%20the%20pink%20of%20your%20health%2C%20how%20will%20you%20live%20up%20to%20the%2014-hour%20shift%20expectations%3F%20It%20is%20important%20to%20move%2C%20get%20those%20steps%20in%2C%20before%20Monday.%20And%20what%20faster%20way%20to%20get%20those%20steps%20in%20than%20walking%20around%20the%20malls%20or%20flea%20markets%20in%20your%20area%3F%20Additionally%2C%20what%20better%20way%20to%20spend%20a%20Sunday%20productively%20than%20shopping%20at%20local%20markets%20and%20helping%20the%20economy%20flourish%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsure%20that%20your%20partner%20is%20with%20you%20so%20they%20can%20stare%20at%20the%20shopkeepers%20and%20their%20wares%20instead%20of%20lovingly%20staring%20at%20you%20(ew).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Productive%20Upskilling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20age%20of%20hustle.%20We%20shouldn't%20be%20wasting%20any%20waking%20moment%20being%20unproductive.%20What%20better%20way%20to%20be%20productive%20than%20to%20upskill%20and%20get%20a%20Sunday%20job%20on%20top%20of%20your%20regular%20job%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatch%20a%20medical%20drama%20to%20start%20a%20hospital%20side%20business%20or%20a%20cooking%20show%20to%20become%20a%20hotelier!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20you%20do%20as%20your%20side%20hustle%2C%20make%20sure%20both%20you%20and%20your%20spouse%20are%20sitting%20on%20a%20cold%2C%20marble%20floor%20without%20any%20back%20support%20because%20comfort%20is%20anathema%20to%20success.%20And%20don't%20forget%20to%20gloat%20on%20LinkedIn%20about%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Productive%20Self-Education%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20are%20never%20too%20old%20to%20educate%20yourself.%20Perhaps%20we%20can%20go%20a%20bit%20old%20school%20for%20this%20one%20and%20utilise%20some%20ancient%20instruments%2C%20called%20books.%20To%20learn%20about%20ancient%20cultures%20and%20lost%20civilisations%2C%20I%20suggest%20%3Cem%3EA%20Song%20Of%20Ice%20And%20Fire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ELord%20Of%20The%20Rings%3C%2Fem%3E.%20For%20Physics%20and%20science%2C%20%3Cem%3EDark%20Matter%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Martian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EHitchhiker's%20Guide%20To%20The%20Galaxy%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20anything%20by%20Isaac%20Asimov%2C%20Arthur%20C%20Clarke%20or%20Michael%20Crichton.%20For%20world%20politics%2C%20try%20Ian%20Fleming%20or%20Graham%20Greene.%20The%20world%20is%20your%20oyster%20if%20only%20you%20stop%20being%20so%20unproductive%20by%20spending%2024%20hours%20staring%20at%20your%20wife.%20Seriously%2C%20why%20do%20you%20even%20want%20to%20look%20at%20her%3F%20Spouses%20are%20not%20meant%20to%20spend%20time%20together.%20That's%20the%20enemy%20of%20nation-building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Get%20Influenced%20By%20CEOs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20clan%20is%20extremely%20focused%20on%20creativity%20and%20productivity.%20The%20reason%20why%20a%20plebian%20like%20myself%20or%20you%20is%20not%20sitting%20in%20a%20bathtub%20full%20of%20cash%20is%20because%20we%20are%20unmoved%2C%20unmotivated%2C%20and%20lazy.%20We%20spend%20our%20free%20time%20doing%20needless%20things%20like%20laundry%2C%20cleaning%20the%20house%2C%20washing%20the%20dishes.%20Learn%20from%20the%20CEOs.%20Like%20that%20one%20Indian-origin%20man%20who%20understands%20that%20his%20time%E2%80%94valued%20at%20%245%2C000%20an%20hour%2C%20by%20himself%E2%80%94is%20too%20precious%20to%20do%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20now.%20There%20will%20be%20some%20kids%20from%20these%20snowflake%20generations%20who%20may%20point%20out%20that%20the%20wealthy%20can%20obviously%20afford%20help%20of%20all%20kinds.%20They%20will%20also%20tell%20you%20that%20not%20everyone%20gets%2024%20hours%20a%20day%20to%20themselves.%20A%20CEO%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20afford%20to%20work%2090%20hours%20a%20week%20because%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20suffer%20household%20chores.%20He%20effectively%20gets%20more%20work%20hours%20than%20the%20average%20Jane%20and%20Joe.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20an%20average%20Joe%20is%20also%20getting%20more%20time%20to%20himself%20than%20an%20average%20Jane.%20Let's%20not%20get%20into%20that%20though.%20Ignore%20the%20%E2%80%98woke'%20mobs.%20Instead%20of%20staring%20at%20your%20spouse%2C%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20doing%20unpaid%20labour%20for%2032%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20handling%20the%20house%2C%20doing%20laundry%2C%20cleaning%2C%20cooking%2C%20feeding%20and%20raising%20the%20children%E2%80%94all%20of%20it%20without%20a%20break%20or%20appreciation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Productive%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20about%20physical%20health%2C%20improving%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20nation-building.%20But%20let's%20be%20honest%2C%20only%20a%20sound%20and%20healthy%20mind%20can%20shoulder%20these%20humongous%20responsibilities.%20The%2090-hour%20workweek%20will%20tire%20out%20those%20little%20grey%20cells%20in%20little%20people.%20Here's%20how%20to%20%E2%80%98Think%20Big'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStop%20caring.%20Empathy%20and%20compassion%20are%20draining%20for%20you%20mentally.%20Hunger%20and%20poverty%20makes%20you%20sad%3F%20Climate%20change%20killing%20your%20hopes%20for%20the%20future%3F%20A%20family%20member%20is%20sick%3F%20A%20coworker%20died%20(learn%20from%20the%20Amazon%20warehouse%20in%20Colorado%20that%20simply%20ignored%20the%20dead%20body%20on%20the%20floor)%3F%20Who%20cares.%20Focus%20on%20that%20spreadsheet%2C%20PPT%2C%20charts%20and%20graphics%20on%20your%20screen%20that%20will%20make%20your%20boss%20millions%20of%20buckaroos%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPay%20no%20attention%20to%20those%20%E2%80%98relaxing%20weekend%20ideas'%20to%20try%20out%20with%20your%20partner.%20This%20is%20not%20some%20utopian%20civilisation%20built%20on%20humans%20and%20culture.%20Here%2C%20we%20remove%20the%20human%20from%20humanity%20to%20ensure%20only%20money%20matters%20in%20the%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Assistant%20Producer%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736581140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ff424hcto_wife_625x300_11_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2F7-productive-things-to-do-instead-of-staring-at-your-wife-on-sundays-7448990%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stop%20caring.%20Empathy%20and%20compassion%20are%20draining%20for%20you%20mentally.%20Focus%20on%20that%20spreadsheet%2C%20PPT%2C%20charts%20and%20graphics%20on%20your%20screen%20that%20will%20make%20your%20boss%20millions%20of%20buckaroos%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2F7-productive-things-to-do-instead-of-staring-at-your-wife-on-sundays-7448990%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22