ulence%20in%20Maharashtra%20continues%20unabated%2C%20even%20after%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Speculation%20is%20rife%20that%20eight%20MPs%20and%20ten%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20are%20poised%20to%20join%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction.%20Reports%20suggest%20these%20legislators%20are%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20group%20and%20may%20announce%20their%20decision%20soon.%20There's%20also%20talk%20of%20a%20potential%20reconciliation%20between%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20whispers%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20himself%20may%20join%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20align%20with%20the%20NDA%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20Efforts%20to%20resolve%20strained%20relationships%20at%20multiple%20levels%20seem%20to%20be%20underway%20to%20facilitate%20this%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20one%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20a%20political%20challenge%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20isolation%20and%20a%20diminishing%20power%20base%20alongside%20his%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20exploring%20new%20permutations%20to%20strike%20the%20best%20possible%20deal.%20As%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%20in%20politics%2C%20anything%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20predicting%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20moves%20is%20no%20easy%20task.%20Political%20observers%20warn%20that%20any%20forecast%20about%20his%20next%20steps%20is%20fraught%20with%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFactors%20Driving%20a%20Reunion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20reconciliation%20began%20with%20a%20plea%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20mother%2C%20who%20urged%20the%20entire%20Pawar%20clan%20to%20come%20together%20following%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20This%20appeal%20was%20followed%20by%20encouraging%20signals%20from%20key%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrashekhar%20Bawankule%2C%20state%20BJP%20chief%20and%20considered%20close%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20recently%20stated%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20no%20objection%20to%20a%20Sharad-Ajit%20reunion.%20Similarly%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20close%20ally%2C%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20has%20expressed%20support%20for%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20a%20rapprochement%20gained%20further%20traction%20after%20the%20UBT-led%20Shiv%20Sena's%20mouthpiece%20Saamana%20praised%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20for%20his%20work%20in%20Naxal-affected%20Gadchiroli.%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20has%20also%20been%20warming%20up%20to%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20buzz%20intensified%20when%20Baramati%20MP%20and%20NCP%20leader%20Supriya%20Sule%20praised%20Chief%20Minister%20Fadnavis%2C%20who%20recently%20assumed%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20person%20who%20is%20working%20very%20hard%20is%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%3B%20no%20one%20else%20is%20visible.%20Devendra%20ji%20is%20focused%20and%20working%20in%20mission%20mode%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%20We%20wish%20him%20all%20the%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Sule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20overtures%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20has%20not%20officially%20confirmed%20any%20move%20toward%20reconciliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20feel%20that%20being%20in%20the%20opposition%20will%20hinder%20development%20work%20in%20their%20constituencies%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20Without%20access%20to%20government%20funds%2C%20they%20may%20struggle%20to%20deliver%20results.%20This%20has%20fuelled%20discussions%20about%20aligning%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amol%20Matele%2C%20state%20spokesperson%20and%20Youth%20Mumbai%20President%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20suggest%20groundwork%20for%20the%20reunion%20is%20already%20underway%2C%20with%20discussions%20taking%20place%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Delhi%20to%20finalize%20the%20alliance.%20The%20primary%20sticking%20point%20remains%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20concerns%20about%20securing%20a%20ministerial%20position%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeighing%20the%20Possibilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leadership%20question%20within%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20been%20resolved%20following%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20success%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20de%20facto%20leader%2C%20a%20status%20cemented%20by%20his%20decision%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20Mahayuti%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20already%20recognized%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20NCP%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20appears%20to%20be%20strategizing%20for%20an%20image-saving%20compromise.%20The%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20(NCP-SP)%20also%20seems%20open%20to%20the%20delineated%20roles%20of%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20a%20possible%20reunited%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20NCP%20was%20united%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%20was%20focused%20on%20national%20politics%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20while%20Ajit%20Pawar%20handled%20key%20decisions%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Party%20workers%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20this%20dynamic.%20The%20idea%20that%20there%20is%20political%20competition%20between%20Sule%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20a%20manufactured%20narrative%20with%20no%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Amol%20Matele.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20NCP(SP)%20MPs%20were%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%2C%20it%20would%20bolster%20the%20NDA's%20strength%20in%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalyzing%20the%20unfolding%20political%20developments%2C%20senior%20journalist%20and%20commentator%20Rohit%20Chandavarkar%20observes%3A%20%26quot%3BThose%20familiar%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar%20believe%20he%20is%20unlikely%20to%20officially%20or%20openly%20align%20with%20the%20NDA%20or%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%20for%20two%20reasons.%20Firstly%2C%20he%20has%20consistently%20upheld%20a%20left-of-center%20ideology.%20In%20every%20rally%2C%20he%20reiterates%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20Mahatma%20Phule%2C%20Chhatrapati%20Sahu%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Ambedkar.%20It's%20unlikely%20he%20will%20abandon%20this%20path%20at%20the%20age%20of%2084.%20Secondly%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20confided%20to%20close%20associates%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20history%20of%20not%20sustaining%20alliances%20with%20its%20partners.%20Look%20at%20what%20happened%20with%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20Pawar%20fears%20that%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%20would%20jeopardize%20long-term%20prospects%20for%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20and%20other%20NCP%20leaders%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20tends%20to%20dominate%20and%20sideline%20its%20allies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20leaders%20from%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)-comprising%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20and%20the%20NCP-have%20dismissed%20the%20rumours%2C%20asserting%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20remains%20committed%20to%20the%20alliance.%20Any%20rapprochement%20with%20the%20BJP%20or%20NDA%20would%20be%20detrimental%20to%20the%20MVA%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20at%20the%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20given%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20political%20style%2C%20few%20are%20willing%20to%20predict%20his%20next%20move.%20%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20limited%20options%20for%20continuing%20as%20an%20independent%20political%20force%20in%20Maharashtra.%20But%2C%20as%20always%20with%20Pawar%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20predicted%20with%20certainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Chandavarkar%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736579220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Flrogfps4_ajit-pawar-sharad-pawar-pti-_625x300_26_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-is-ncp-reunion-around-the-corner-7448893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Political%20turbulence%20in%20Maharashtra%20continues%20unabated%2C%20even%20after%20the%20assembly%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-is-ncp-reunion-around-the-corner-7448893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Chief%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20With%20Rs%20544%20Crore%20Salary%2C%20Gets%2018%25%20Pay%20Rise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20Inc.%20disclosed%20an%2018%25%20pay%20increase%20for%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Tim%20Cook%20ahead%20of%20its%20annual%20meeting%20next%20month%2C%20while%20also%20saying%20it%20opposed%20a%20shareholder%20measure%20calling%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20company's%20diversity%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cook's%20compensation%20grew%20to%20%2474.6%20million%20(Rs%20643%20crore)%20in%202024%2C%20compared%20with%20%2463.2%20million%20(Rs%20544%20crore)%20the%20prior%20year%2C%20Apple%20said%20in%20its%20annual%20proxy%20filing%20on%20Friday.%20In%20addition%20to%20executive%20compensation%2C%20investors%20will%20vote%20on%20four%20outside%20proposals%20at%20the%20meeting%20on%20February%2025.%20The%20company%20opposed%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measure%20about%20Apple's%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%2C%20or%20DEI%2C%20efforts%20urged%20the%20company%20to%20consider%20abolishing%20the%20program%20because%20it%20may%20discriminate%20against%20employees%20and%20draw%20lawsuits.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20proposal%20was%20an%20inappropriate%20attempt%20to%20restrict%20Apple's%20business%20operations%20and%20that%20it%20alr