s%20to%20bed%20and%20then%20went%20to%20bed%20early%20ourselves%2C%20around%208%20p.m.%20We%20knew%20we%20weren't%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20sleep.%20Outside%20the%20back%20of%20our%20home%2C%20we%20could%20see%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fla-wildfire-pacific-palisades-evacuees-share-devastation-town-gone-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPalisades%20fire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20getting%20closer%20and%20closer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20definitely%20wasn't%20the%20best%20sleep%2C%20but%20I%20managed%20to%20get%20some%20shut-eye.%20Then%2C%20at%20about%204%3A30%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20we%20got%20an%20alert%20that%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurviving-marshall-fire-colorado-what-los-angeles-should-expect-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eneeded%20to%20evacuate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228abfca6e-ad44-4b46-b87a-ad34ae8a6b69%5C%22%3EOur%20bags%20were%20already%20packed%20when%20we%20got%20the%20alert%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20already%20packed%20essentials%20like%20clothing%2C%20a%20few%20of%20the%20boys'%20favorite%20toys%2C%20and%20my%20wife's%20breast%20pump%2C%20plus%20our%20important%20documents%20like%20birth%20certificates.%20We%20grabbed%20the%20bags%20and%20our%20sons%2C%20who%20are%2010%20months%20and%205%20years%20old%2C%20and%20drove%20to%20my%20in-laws'%20house%20in%20Studio%20City%2C%20near%20where%20I%20practice%20pediatrics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20older%20son%20was%20excited%20to%20have%20a%20day%20with%20his%20grandparents.%20We%20talked%20with%20him%20a%20bit%20about%20the%20fires%20and%20he%20could%20see%20the%20smoke%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20really%20understand%20what%20was%20going%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20Friday%20the%20evacuation%20order%20for%20our