ndia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20salute%20to%20his%20resolve%2C%20Billy%20Arjan%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%201995%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20gold%20medal%20by%20the%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%20(1996).%20In%201997%2C%20he%20became%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20Order%20of%20the%20Golden%20Ark%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Dutch%20order%20of%20merit%3B%20in%202004%20he%20won%20the%20J.Paul%20Getty%20Wildlife%20Conservation%20Award%3B%20and%20in%202006%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20and%20the%20Yash%20Bharati%20Award.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fphoto%252F%253Ffbid%253D456683486504283%2526set%253Da.456683459837619%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20glint%20of%20the%20awards%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20Billy%20Arjan%20had%20each%20time%20a%20tiger%20lived%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20Today%2C%20the%20landscape%20of%20Dudhwa%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%94%20a%20490%20sq%20km%20park%20established%20in%201977%2C%20which%20connects%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F223054%2Fkerala-forest-department-tiger-sreenivasan-earth-hero-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportant%20tiger%20habitats%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20India%20and%20Nepal%20%E2%80%94%20is%20decorated%20with%20elephants%2C%20rhinos%2C%20over%2045%20species%20of%20birds%20and%20of%20course%2C%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommending%20his%20passion%2C%20Brinda%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20always%20knew%20him%20as%20a%20person%20of%20tremendous%20belief.%20We%20were%20always%20proud%20of%20him.%E2%80%9D%20Brinda%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20at%20Tiger%20Haven%20Society%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20champion%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20life%2C%20why%20anyone%20would%20want%20to%20hunt%20down%20an%20animal%20that%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20ecosystem%20was%20an%20enigma%20to%20him.%20And%2C%20till%20his%20last%20breath%2C%20he%20maintained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20air%20we%20breathe%20and%20the%20water%20we%20drink%20stem%20from%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20universal%20environment%20and%20its%20economics.%20The%20tiger%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20truth.%20If%20it%20goes%2C%20we%20go.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESpecial%20thanks%20to%20Amith%20Bangre%2C%20General%20Manager%20and%20Chief%20Naturalist%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjaagirmanor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJaagir%20Manor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20his%20invaluable%20support%20in%20arranging%20interviews%20and%20providing%20crucial%20assistance%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wwfindia.org%2F%3F3880%2FTiger-walla-departs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Billy%E2%80%99%20Arjan%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20the%20legendary%20%E2%80%98Tiger-walla%E2%80%99%20departs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20WWF%20India%2C%20Published%20on%206%20January%202010.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-billy-arjan-singh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeet%20Billy%20Arjan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Sanctuary%20Asia%2C%20Published%20in%20September%202000.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-bloc